const INITIAL_STATE={
  title:'',
  author:'',
  body: '',
  image: '',
  summary: '',
  secret:'',
  state: '',
  tags: '',
  featured: false,
  instagram: '',
  lat: '',
  lng: '',
  zoom: 9
}



export default function(state=[] , action){
 switch(action.type){
   case 'INITIAL_STATE':
     return action.payload

   default:
     return state
 }
}
